@startuml
left to right direction

skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FEFECE
    BorderColor #A80036
}

'-------------- Actors -------------
"Data Scientist" as DS #lightyellow
"ML Provider" as MLProvider
"ML Consumer" as MLConsumer
note bottom of MLProvider : Publishes the consolidated \nresults of Data Scientist and ML engineer work.
"ML Engineer" as Dev #lightgreen
"Domain Expert" as DomainExpert #lightgreen

DS <|-- MLProvider
Dev <|-- MLProvider


' ------------- Use Cases -------------
'Préciser les requirements FATEs du ML
rectangle "FATEs Justification System" as FS {
    CollectReq as (Collect FATEs requirements) #lightgreen
    GenJustModel as (Generate a Justification Model) #lightgreen
    Verify as (Check FATEs properties) #lightgreen
    GenJust as (Generate Justification) #lightgreen

    CollectEvidence as (Collect evidence) #lightgreen
    InstrumentCI as (Instrument the CI/CD pipeline to justify) #lightgreen

    DefineRule as (Define new FATES rules to check) #lightgreen
}
'note top of FS : Defines the framework for verifying FATES properties
rectangle "PROFIL system" as PS{
    CheckQuality as (Check Quality) #lightyellow
    Explore as (Explore the ML landscape) #lightyellow
    Instrument as (Define new quality rules to check) #lightyellow
    'GenDoc as (Generate Documentation)
    'BasedOnConstruction as (based on construction criteria) #lightblue
    ExtractMLProfile as (Extract ML descriptions from code) #lightyellow
    CheckMLArchitecture as (Check ML architecture) #lightyellow
    CheckMLCode as (Check ML code quality) #lightyellow
}
note bottom of PS : Engine for \nlinting and static analysis



rectangle "Exploration System" as ES {
    Compare as (Compare/filter/Analyse ML system) #lightblue
    CompareConstruction as (according to Construction Criteria) #lightblue
    CompareFATES as (according to FATES properties) #lightblue
    'Register as (Register a ML description) #lightblue
    Manage as (Manage ML descriptions) #lightblue
    Generate as (Write/Generate ML description) #lightblue
    CheckMLDescription as (Check ML description) #lightblue


 }
Compare <.. CompareConstruction :extends
Compare <.. CompareFATES :extends
MLConsumer --> Compare
MLProvider --> Manage
MLConsumer --> CheckMLDescription
MLProvider --> CheckMLDescription

DS --|>MLConsumer





'-------------- Relations -------------
'domaine expert
':DomainExpert: --> CollectReq
:DomainExpert: --> GenJustModel
GenJustModel <.. CollectReq :extends
:DomainExpert: --> (Audit Justification)

'ML developer
:Dev: --> CollectEvidence
:Dev: --> InstrumentCI
':Dev: --> Verify
InstrumentCI --> Verify:includes
'InstrumentCI --> GenJust:includes
CompareConstruction <.. CheckQuality :extends
CheckMLArchitecture --|> CheckQuality
CheckMLCode --|> CheckQuality
'note on link : FATEs verification specializes \ngeneric quality checks
':Dev: --> GenJust

'ML provider
':MLProvider: --> GenDoc

Manage<..Generate   :extends
'Manage<..Extract   :extends
'Manage<..Register   :extends
'Generate <.. Register :extends

 Manage <.. GenJust :extends
'Explore <..  Extract :extends

'Extract <|-- BasedOnConstruction
 CheckMLDescription--> Verify : includes

'-------------- Data Scientist -------------
DS --> Explore
DS --> Instrument
DS --> CheckQuality
DS --> DefineRule
DS --> ExtractMLProfile




@enduml
Dev --> (Filter LLMs by business criteria)
DS --> (Filter LLMs Based on Model Construction Criteria )
DS --> (Compare LLMs according to Construction Criteria)
DS --> (Check some properties of LLMs)
DS --> (Explore LLM Documentation)
(Compare LLMs according to Construction Criteria) <.. (Visualize the LLM Construction Workflow):extends
Admin --> (Enrich the LLM Metadata Schema )
Admin --> (Configure Verification-Based LLM Criteria)
DS --> (Compare LLM Construction Workflows)
(Compare LLM Construction Workflows) <.. (Visualize the LLM Construction Workflow):extends

